Name: Basic Kao Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Runestone, Wisdom 13 Or Greater
Description: This rune symbolizes ill intent, lasting suffering, and misfortune. It is commonly known as the rune of curses, allowing those who wield it the ability to inflict calamity upon their foes.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACECurse of SpeedSPACEAs an action, you attempt to curse a target within DISTANCE15-30DISTANCE feet of you. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be forced to take the Dash action on their next turn, expending all of their available movement if possible. A creature that succeeds on its saving throw is immune to this effect for the next 24 hours.SPACESPACEYou may use this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 1 runic attunement slot.
